  <summary date="2023-04-24T18:40:04Z" status="Introduced in House">Stop CRT Act

This bill grants Executive Order 13950 the force and effect of law. That order prohibits federal agencies and contractors from advancing specified policies or training related to race or sex and was revoked by Executive Order 13985 on January 20, 2021.</summary>
